com.github.webapp_minifier.options

Interface OverridablePluginOptions

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PluginOptions
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultOverridablePluginOptions, WebappMinifierMojo

    public interface OverridablePluginOptions
    This interface defines the plugin options that can be overridable.
